docs/combat_authority_map.md:41:2. `src/combat/turn_system/mod.rs` reads `ActionIntent`, performs legality checks, emits action lifecycle events, and emits live `OnCombatBeat` markers.
docs/combat_authority_map.md:46:The live emitted events include `OnActionDeclared`, `OnActionPreApp`, `OnCombatBeat`, `OnKernelTransition`, `OnActionApplied`, `OnActionResolved`, and failure variants such as `OnActionFailed`. `OnCombatBeat` and the mirrored `CombatKernelTransition::Beat` are live during action resolution; they are not just typed vocabulary.
