docs/combat_mixed_pattern_drift_ledger.md:78:**Handoff note:** R097 separates typed beat vocabulary from gameplay authority. `OnCombatBeat` is live and synchronized, but presentation fields such as `animation_sequence` and `qte` remain non-authoritative until a later slice proves otherwise.
